{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Transformer 架构入门\n",
    "\n",
    "本笔记对应论文：*Attention Is All You Need*（Vaswani et al., 2017）\n",
    "\n",
    "## 目标\n",
    "- 理解 Transformer 的整体结构\n",
    "- 动手实现自注意力（Self-Attention）核心计算\n",
    "- 理解为什么注意力机制取代了 RNN"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 为什么需要 Transformer？\n",
    "\n",
    "在 Transformer 之前，序列建模主要依赖 **RNN（循环神经网络）**：\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "x₁ → h₁ → x₂ → h₂ → x₃ → h₃ → ...\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**RNN 的两大问题：**\n",
    "1. **串行计算**：必须按顺序处理，无法并行，训练慢\n",
    "2. **长程依赖问题**：序列长度增大后，早期信息在隐状态中被稀释\n",
    "\n",
    "Transformer 用 **注意力机制** 解决了这两个问题：\n",
    "- 所有位置同时计算（并行）\n",
    "- 任意两个位置之间的距离都是 1（直接建立连接）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Transformer 整体架构\n",
    "\n",
    "原始 Transformer 是编码器-解码器（Encoder-Decoder）结构，用于机器翻译。\n",
    "现代 LLM（GPT 系列）只使用**解码器（Decoder-Only）**部分。\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
    "│           Decoder Block × N         │\n",
    "│  ┌─────────────────────────────┐    │\n",
    "│  │  Masked Multi-Head Attention│    │\n",
    "│  │  + Add & Norm               │    │\n",
    "│  │  Feed-Forward Network       │    │\n",
    "│  │  + Add & Norm               │    │\n",
    "│  └─────────────────────────────┘    │\n",
    "└─────────────────────────────────────┘\n",
    "         ↑\n",
    "Token Embeddings + Positional Encoding\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心组件：**\n",
    "| 组件 | 作用 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| Token Embedding | 将 token id 转为向量 |\n",
    "| Positional Encoding | 注入位置信息（注意力本身无位置感知）|\n",
    "| Multi-Head Attention | 让每个 token 关注序列中其他 token |\n",
    "| Feed-Forward Network | 对每个位置独立的两层 MLP |\n",
    "| Layer Norm + Residual | 稳定训练，缓解梯度消失 |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 自注意力（Self-Attention）核心计算\n",
    "\n",
    "### 直觉理解\n",
    "\n",
    "对于句子 \"**The animal didn't cross the street because it was too tired**\"，\n",
    "模型需要理解 \"it\" 指的是 \"animal\" 而不是 \"street\"。\n",
    "自注意力让 \"it\" 能够直接"看向"并赋予 \"animal\" 更高权重。\n",
    "\n",
    "### 数学公式\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{Attention}(Q, K, V) = \\text{softmax}\\left(\\frac{QK^T}{\\sqrt{d_k}}\\right)V$$\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Q（Query）**：当前 token 在"问什么"\n",
    "- **K（Key）**：每个 token 在"提供什么标签"\n",
    "- **V（Value）**：每个 token 实际携带的信息\n",
    "- **$\\sqrt{d_k}$**：缩放因子，防止点积过大导致 softmax 梯度消失"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "def softmax(x, axis=-1):\n",
    "    e = np.exp(x - x.max(axis=axis, keepdims=True))\n",
    "    return e / e.sum(axis=axis, keepdims=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "def scaled_dot_product_attention(Q, K, V, mask=None):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    Q, K, V: shape (seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "    returns: output (seq_len, d_k), attention_weights (seq_len, seq_len)\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    d_k = Q.shape[-1]\n",
    "    scores = Q @ K.T / np.sqrt(d_k)      # (seq_len, seq_len)\n",
    "    if mask is not None:\n",
    "        scores = np.where(mask, scores, -1e9)\n",
    "    weights = softmax(scores)             # 每行和为 1\n",
    "    output = weights @ V                  # (seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "    return output, weights\n",
    "\n",
    "# 示例：3 个 token，d_k=4\n",
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
    "seq_len, d_k = 3, 4\n",
    "Q = np.random.randn(seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "K = np.random.randn(seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "V = np.random.randn(seq_len, d_k)\n",
    "\n",
    "output, weights = scaled_dot_product_attention(Q, K, V)\n",
    "print(\"注意力权重矩阵（每行代表一个 token 对其他 token 的关注度）：\")\n",
    "print(np.round(weights, 3))\n",
    "print(\"\\n每行之和（应为 1.0）：\", weights.sum(axis=-1).round(3))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 因果掩码（Causal Mask）\n",
    "\n",
    "在解码器（Decoder-Only LLM）中，生成第 t 个 token 时只能看到位置 ≤ t 的 token，\n",
    "不能"偷看"未来——这通过**下三角掩码**实现："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 因果掩码：下三角为 True（可见），上三角为 False（屏蔽）\n",
    "causal_mask = np.tril(np.ones((seq_len, seq_len), dtype=bool))\n",
    "print(\"因果掩码：\")\n",
    "print(causal_mask.astype(int))\n",
    "\n",
    "output_causal, weights_causal = scaled_dot_product_attention(Q, K, V, mask=causal_mask)\n",
    "print(\"\\n应用掩码后的注意力权重：\")\n",
    "print(np.round(weights_causal, 3))\n",
    "# 注意：第一行只能看自己，第二行能看前两个，第三行能看全部"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. 多头注意力（Multi-Head Attention）\n",
    "\n",
    "单头注意力只能关注一种模式。多头注意力将 $d_{model}$ 分成 $h$ 个头，\n",
    "每个头学习不同的关注模式（语法、语义、指代...），最后拼接：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{MultiHead}(Q,K,V) = \\text{Concat}(\\text{head}_1,...,\\text{head}_h)W^O$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{head}_i = \\text{Attention}(QW_i^Q, KW_i^K, VW_i^V)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def multi_head_attention(X, W_q, W_k, W_v, W_o, num_heads):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    X: (seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "    W_q/k/v: (d_model, d_model)\n",
    "    W_o: (d_model, d_model)\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    seq_len, d_model = X.shape\n",
    "    d_k = d_model // num_heads\n",
    "\n",
    "    Q = X @ W_q  # (seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "    K = X @ W_k\n",
    "    V = X @ W_v\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 拆分多头\n",
    "    Q = Q.reshape(seq_len, num_heads, d_k).transpose(1, 0, 2)  # (heads, seq, d_k)\n",
    "    K = K.reshape(seq_len, num_heads, d_k).transpose(1, 0, 2)\n",
    "    V = V.reshape(seq_len, num_heads, d_k).transpose(1, 0, 2)\n",
    "\n",
    "    heads = []\n",
    "    for i in range(num_heads):\n",
    "        out, _ = scaled_dot_product_attention(Q[i], K[i], V[i])\n",
    "        heads.append(out)\n",
    "\n",
    "    concat = np.concatenate(heads, axis=-1)  # (seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "    return concat @ W_o\n",
    "\n",
    "d_model, num_heads = 8, 2\n",
    "X = np.random.randn(seq_len, d_model)\n",
    "W_q = np.random.randn(d_model, d_model) * 0.1\n",
    "W_k = np.random.randn(d_model, d_model) * 0.1\n",
    "W_v = np.random.randn(d_model, d_model) * 0.1\n",
    "W_o = np.random.randn(d_model, d_model) * 0.1\n",
    "\n",
    "mha_out = multi_head_attention(X, W_q, W_k, W_v, W_o, num_heads)\n",
    "print(f\"输入形状: {X.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"多头注意力输出形状: {mha_out.shape}  (与输入相同)\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. 用 PyTorch 验证\n",
    "\n",
    "PyTorch 内置了 `nn.MultiheadAttention`，与我们手动实现的逻辑完全一致："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "\n",
    "d_model, num_heads, seq_len = 64, 8, 10\n",
    "mha = nn.MultiheadAttention(embed_dim=d_model, num_heads=num_heads, batch_first=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "x = torch.randn(1, seq_len, d_model)  # (batch, seq, d_model)\n",
    "output, attn_weights = mha(x, x, x)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"输入形状:  {x.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"输出形状:  {output.shape}\")\n",
    "print(f\"注意力权重形状: {attn_weights.shape}  (batch, seq, seq)\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. 小结\n",
    "\n",
    "| 概念 | 要点 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| 自注意力 | 每个 token 对所有 token 计算相关度，加权求和 |\n",
    "| 缩放因子 $\\sqrt{d_k}$ | 防止点积过大，稳定梯度 |\n",
    "| 因果掩码 | 解码器生成时只能看过去，不能看未来 |\n",
    "| 多头注意力 | 并行多个注意力头，捕获不同语义模式 |\n",
    "\n",
    "## 下一篇\n",
    "\n",
